snippet.title: Rhapsody: Marl Kingdom Chronicles - Rhapsody III Spotlight | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Rhapsody III: Memories of Marl Kingdom concludes the stories of Rhapsody and its characters in a charming collection of chapters. Experience events that occur before, during, and after the previous Rhapsody titles, and dive into the revamped battle system with combined character attacks and the addition of a 3D camera.

Rhapsody: Marl Kingdom Chronicles comes August 29, 2023 to PS5! 

#ps5 #ps5games
